	<text>
		<body>
			<div type="transcription">
				<div type="original" xml:lang="cs">
					<pb facs="EHRI-DC-032_01.png" n="1"/>
					<p><placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/3067696/prague.html">Praha</placeName>, dne <date when-iso="1945-11-15">15. listopadu 1945</date></p>
					<p><term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/terezin-terms-keyword-jmp-657" type="subject">DOKUMENTAČNÍ AKCE</term></p>
					<p><orgName ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/authorities/ehri_cb-400">Jewish Agency for Palestine</orgName></p>
					<p>EZRA KOMITÉT PRO ČSR</p>
					<p><placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/3067696/prague.html">Praha</placeName> V., <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/3067696/prague.html">Josefovská 7</placeName>. tel. 620-02</p>
					<p><term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-1055" type="subject">Statistické</term> údaje k <q>pokoji</q></p>
					<p>Přednostní lepší <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-837" type="subject">ubytování</term> (<term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-824" type="subject">dětské</term>
						<term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-837" type="subject">pokoje</term> atd.)</p>
					<p>počet <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-837" type="subject">ubytovaných</term>: 12</p>
					<p>rozměry: 6 x 4 m … 34 m2 t.j. 2 m2 na 1 osobu (teoreticky) po odečtení inventáře v rozměru 10.7 m2 zbývá fakticky <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-837" type="subject">obytná</term> plocha na 1 osobu … 1.1 m2</p>
					<p><term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-831" type="subject">prostor</term>: 6 x 4 x 3.20 m … 76.8 m3 (teoreticky)po odečtení obsahu inventáře asi 4.8 m3 zbývá faktický <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-831" type="subject"
							>prostor</term> 72 m3 pro 12 osobčili 6 m3 pro 1 osobu na 12 hodin na 1 osobu a na 1 hodinu ….. 0.5 m3 <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-831" type="subject">vzduchu</term>!</p>
					<p>vzhledem k nedostatečnému zásobování uhlím bývala okna většinou zavřena.</p>
					<p>Modelář:</p>
					<p><persName ref="#ehri_dc_lauscher_jiri">Jiří Lauscher</persName></p>
					<p><term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/terezin-terms-keyword-jmp-657" type="subject">Dokumentační akce</term>: <persName ref="#ehri_dc_shek_zeev">Scheck</persName></p>
					<pb facs="EHRI-DC-032_02.png" n="2"/>
					<p><date when="1945-11-16">16. XI. 1945</date></p>
					<p><persName ref="#ehri_dc_schmiedt_alexander">Alex Schmiedt</persName></p>
					<pb facs="EHRI-DC-032_03.png" n="3"/>
					<p>Protokol</p>
					<p>sepsaný s panem <persName ref="#ehri_dc_lauscher_jiri">Jiřím Lauscherem</persName>, nar. <date when="1901-09-15">15. 9. 1901</date> v <placeName ref="https://www.geonames.org/3064268/terezin.html">Terezíně</placeName>, <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-837" type="subject">bytem</term> v <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/3067696/prague.html">Praze</placeName> VII., <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/3067696/prague.html">Heřmanova 43</placeName>,
						národnosti židovské, povoláním soukromý <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-1111" type="subject">úředník</term>, bývalým <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-483" type="subject">vězněm</term> z <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-496" type="subject">koncentr.</term>
						<term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-496" type="subject">tábora</term>
						<placeName ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_ghettos-449" type="ghetto">Terezín</placeName> - <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-545" type="subject">ghetto</term>.</p>
					<p>Předávám různé <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-673" type="subject">umělecko</term> - <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-937" type="subject">průmyslové</term> výrobky, jejichž unikáty byly vyrobeny v <placeName
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_ghettos-449" type="ghetto">Terezíně</placeName> jako dárkové předměty. Podle těchto vzorů vyrobil jsem větší počet předmětů pro <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/terezin-terms-keyword-jmp-657"
							type="subject">dokumentační akci</term>
						<term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/terezin-terms-keyword-jmp-657" type="subject">akci</term>.</p>
					<p>Podpis:</p>
					<p><persName ref="#ehri_dc_lauscher_jiri">Jiří Lauscher</persName></p>
					<p>Protokol přijal:</p>
					<p><persName ref="#ehri_dc_schickova_helena">Helena Schicková</persName></p>
					<p>Podpis svědků: <persName ref="#ehri_dc_saxlova_edita">Dita Saxlová</persName></p>
					<p><persName ref="#ehri_dc_gerzonova_berta">Berta Gerzonová</persName></p>
					<p>Za <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/terezin-terms-keyword-jmp-657" type="subject">dokumentační akci</term> přijal:</p>
					<p>
						<persName ref="#ehri_dc_shek_zeev">Scheck</persName></p>
					<p>Za archiv:</p>
					<p><persName ref="#ehri_dc_schmiedt_alexander">Alex. Schmiedt</persName></p>
					<p><date when="1945-10-19">19. 10. 1945</date></p>
					<pb facs="EHRI-DC-032_04.png" n="4"/>
					<p>Modely <placeName ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_ghettos-449" type="ghetto">terezínského</placeName>
						<term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-837" type="subject">pokoje</term> jsou v přesném měřítku 1:10. <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-837" type="subject">Pokoj</term> představuje <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-837" type="subject">ubytování</term> přednostní např. pro <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-827" type="subject">mládež</term>, pokud nebyli umístěni v <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-315" type="subject">domovech</term>.</p>
					<p>Modely <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-837" type="subject">obydlí</term>
						<term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-837" type="subject">Erdbunkeru</term> jsou v měřítku 1:20. Stavba střechy je zjednodušena, neboť se v této velikosti špatně provádí do podrobnosti. Náčrtek znázorňuje skutečnou konstrukci. Práce není dílenská,
						nýbrž modely jsou zhotoveny primitivními pomůckami.</p>
					<pb facs="EHRI-DC-032_05.png" n="5"/>
					<p><note type="gloss">[samostatný list nákresu <q><term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-837" type="subject">Erdbunkeru</term></q>]</note></p>
				</div>
				<div type="translation" xml:lang="en">
					<pb facs="EHRI-DC-032_01.png" n="1"/>
					<p><placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/3067696/prague.html">Prague</placeName>, on <date when="1945-11-15">November 15th, 1945</date></p>
					<p><term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/terezin-terms-keyword-jmp-657" type="subject">DOCUMENTATION CAMPAIGN</term></p>
					<p><orgName ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/authorities/ehri_cb-400">Jewish Agency for Palestine</orgName>.</p>
					<p>EZRA COMMITTEE FOR THE CSR</p>
					<p><placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/3067696/prague.html">Prague</placeName> V., <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/3067696/prague.html">Josefovská 7</placeName>. tel. 620-02</p>
					<p><term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-1055" type="subject">Statistics</term> on the <q>rooms</q></p>
					<p>Preferential better <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-837" type="subject">housing</term> (<term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-824" type="subject">children’s</term>
						<term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-837" type="subject">rooms</term>, etc.)</p>
					<p>Number of <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-837" type="subject">inhabitants</term>: 12</p>
					<p>Size: 6 x 4 m … 34 sq. m. i.e. 2 sq. m. per person (theoretically) after subtracting the furniture, sized 10.7 sq. m., the actual <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-837" type="subject">residential</term> area per person is … 1.1 sq. m.</p>
					<p><term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-831" type="subject">space</term>: 6 x 4 x 3.20 m … 76.8 m3 (theoretically), after subtracting the furniture, sized about 4.8 m3, the actual <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-831"
							type="subject">space</term> is 72 m3 for 12 peopleor 6 m3 per person for 12 hours for 1 person and for 1 hour ….. 0.5 m3 of <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-831" type="subject">air</term>!</p>
					<p>Due to insufficient supplies of coal, the windows often remained closed.</p>
					<p>Modeller:</p>
					<p><persName ref="#ehri_dc_lauscher_jiri">Jiří Lauscher</persName></p>
					<p><term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/terezin-terms-keyword-jmp-657" type="subject">Documentation Campaign</term>: <persName ref="#ehri_dc_shek_zeev">Scheck</persName></p>
					<pb facs="EHRI-DC-032_02.png" n="2"/>
					<p><date when="1945-11-16">16. XI. 1945</date></p>
					<p><persName ref="#ehri_dc_schmiedt_alexander">Alex Schmiedt</persName></p>
					<pb facs="EHRI-DC-032_03.png" n="3"/>
					<p>Statement</p>
					<p>Written with Mr. <persName ref="#ehri_dc_lauscher_jiri">Jiří Lauscher</persName>, born <date when="1901-09-15">15. 9. 1901</date> in <placeName ref="https://www.geonames.org/3064268/terezin.html">Theresienstadt</placeName>, <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-837" type="subject">residing</term> in <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/3067696/prague.html">Prague</placeName> VII., <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/3067696/prague.html">Heřmanova 43</placeName>,
						Jewish nationality, profession private <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-1111" type="subject">civil servant</term>, former <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-483" type="subject">prisoner</term> of the <placeName
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_ghettos-449" type="ghetto">Theresienstadt</placeName> - <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-545" type="subject">ghetto</term>
						<term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-496" type="subject">concentr</term>. <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-496" type="subject">camp</term>.</p>
					<p>I am handing over various <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-673" type="subject">applied</term> - <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-937" type="subject">art</term> articles modeled on the originals that were manufactured in
							<placeName ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_ghettos-449" type="ghetto">Theresienstadt</placeName> as gifts. I have created a large number of these articles for the <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/terezin-terms-keyword-jmp-657"
							type="subject">documentation campaign</term>.</p>
					<p>Signature:</p>
					<p><persName ref="#ehri_dc_lauscher_jiri">Jiří Lauscher</persName></p>
					<p>Statement accepted by:</p>
					<p><persName ref="#ehri_dc_schickova_helena">Helena Schicková</persName></p>
					<p>Signature of witnesses: <persName ref="#ehri_dc_saxlova_edita">Dita Saxlová</persName></p>
					<p><persName ref="#ehri_dc_gerzonova_berta">Berta Gerzonová</persName></p>
					<p>On behalf of the <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/terezin-terms-keyword-jmp-657" type="subject">documentation campaign</term>:</p>
					<p><persName ref="#ehri_dc_shek_zeev">Scheck</persName></p>
					<p>On behalf of the archive:</p>
					<p><persName ref="#ehri_dc_schmiedt_alexander">Alex. Schmiedt</persName></p>
					<p><date when="1945-10-19">19. 10. 1945</date></p>
					<pb facs="EHRI-DC-032_04.png" n="4"/>
					<p>Model of a <placeName ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_ghettos-449" type="ghetto">Theresienstadt</placeName>
						<term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-837" type="subject">room</term> at an exact scale of 1:10. The <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-837" type="subject">room</term> shows preferential <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-837" type="subject">housing</term>, for example for <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-827" type="subject">youths</term> if they weren’t placed in <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-315" type="subject">houses</term>.</p>
					<p>Model of <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-837" type="subject">housing</term> in the <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-837" type="subject">Erdbunker</term> at a scale of 1:20. The roof has been simplified because at this
						size the details wouldn’t be seen. The sketch depicts the actual building. It was not produced in a workshop. The models have been created with primitive tools.</p>
					<pb facs="EHRI-DC-032_05.png" n="5"/>
					<p><note type="gloss">[single page with the <q><term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-837" type="subject">Erdbunker</term></q> sketch]</note></p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</body>
